        "zh": "1.企業研究目標<br>2.研究程序<br>3.研究倫理<br>4.研究設計<br>5.研究方法<br>6.研究測量<br>7.研究分析<br>8.研究寫作<br>",
        "en": "1.Business research objectives<br>2.Research procedures<br>3.Research ethics<br>4.Research designs<br>5.Research methodologies<br>6.Measurement<br>7.Data analysis tools<br>8.Report writing<br>"
